<div class="title">Help When You Need It</div>
<div class="substance">Diazepam (Valium)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=KA&Exact=1">KA</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; KA. "Help When You Need It: An Experience with Diazepam (Valium) (exp5982)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jan 18, 2002. erowid.org/exp/5982</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
